                  
#### To prevent cross-site forgery:  ####            
                  
            {% csrf_token %}

eg.
<form action="{% url 'register' %}" method="POST">
                    {% csrf_token %}
                  <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="first_name">First Name</label>
                  <input type="text" name="first_name" class="form-control" required>
                </div>

##### the presence of the token can be verified in the Console=>Elements near the form field. eg:

<input type="hidden" name="csrfmiddlewaretoken" value="8Jmlq6onga0YAaUsInULGuUkMK590SSZDn1yCE3vugxSwjU25BacccbsKr3vZmAq">